  "title": "Partner Alliance Executive / Senior Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Build, nurture, and expand strategic relationships with existing partners while onboarding new ones to drive business growth.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with partners, sales, and presales teams to accelerate engagement and execution.</p></li><li><p>Partner with startups and vendors to align on technology roadmaps and initiatives.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with founders, market researchers, and ecosystem stakeholders to understand market trends and emerging technologies.</p></li><li><p>Translate insights from market dynamics and internal capabilities into actionable business strategies.</p></li><li><p>Lead internal teams in exploring emerging technologies and developing innovative solutions.</p></li><li><p>Analyze data to identify trends and opportunities that support strategic decision-making.</p></li><li><p>Prepare clear, actionable reports, dashboards, and presentations for management review.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Relevant experience in IT, technology innovation, or partner management.</p></li><li><p>Strong skills in strategic collaboration, market analysis, and cross-functional coordination.</p></li><li><p>Ability to translate complex insights into actionable recommendations.</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and relationship-building skills.</p></li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Work Location: </strong>Tampines <br /></p><p></p><p>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)</p><p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>kayla@talentsis.com.sg</strong> for immediate processing.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
